resented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 13.655856, "shard": "09", "shelf_id": "sn84036285, 1930-09-18, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/mthi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["united states", "red lodge", "montana", "carbon"], "subject_headings": ["United States--Montana--Carbon--Red Lodge"], "subjects": [{"carbon": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:carbon&fo=json"}, {"montana": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:montana&fo=json"}, {"red lodge": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:red+lodge&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-07-06T01:53:56.989Z", "title": "The Carbon County news (Red Lodge, Mont.), September 18, 1930", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036285/1930-09-18/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036285/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn84036285", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/1bf49fe7-6ef1-5222-9d5b-571a9d76d778"], "batch": ["mthi_goosefoot_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1924", "description": ["Weekly Vol. 1, no. 33 (Nov. 6, 1924)-v. 8, no. 31 (Oct. 3, 1931). \"Republican.\" Cf. Directory of Montana newspapers, 1925-1931. \"Official paper of the City of Red Lodge,\" 1926-1931; \"official paper of Carbon County,\" 1927-1931. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling Americ